reviewText: Molly takes a "hands-on" approach to getting that young body middle-aged housewives quietly yearn for.  She is not afraid to get her hands dirty, and takes particular interest in the hip and groin area.  (The included tape measure is essential to make absolutely sure that young body of yours truly MEASURES UP.)

Molly's next video involves mentoring teenage boys. It features a 15 year old child recieving her services. Apparently she is like the horse whisperer for teens. Watch for local law enforcement to be releasing it soon.
